b> DOUBLE</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--> damage with my critical nukes, that it saves me mana and time- be it soloing in groups. Plus it kicks ass in a raid situation when all of a sudden BLAM 3k, or 4k a nuke. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br><br>I have 4 points currently brewing right now, which I will be putting into Exodus once I get the next two points. Why? Besides the fact that they just shaved off the 1 second casting time (down to .1 sec now), it's main use is to get the hell out of a situation NOW. This is great in AOE groups, when you have 15 - 35 mobs just sitting around, and the enchanter happens to bite the big one. 9 seconds for Evacuation before was just laughable, because you know as well as anyone else that you are dogmeat within 3 seconds of the enchanter dying. This gives you a viable escape IF the enchanter dies. I like that. I don't like being dead.<br><br>Before this, I was almost going to do Manaburn, but ran into a hitch. With manaburn you have to put 3 skills into Mental Clarity, and while that's moderately useful.. its 12 extra points! Plus the 5 for Manaburn and thats 17 points! For 18, you can put it all into Spell Casting Fury Master 3 and have a better chance to crit nuke instead of Manaburn.<br><br>Anyway.. I'm at work, decided to spark a conversation, but break is over and I got to go.. heheh.<br><br><br> <p><br><br><p><img src="http://publish.hometown.aol.com/slytlidisturbed/images/vaeluudar.jpg"></p><p align="center"><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=60323">Vaeluudar's Profile</a></p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#f7f7f7><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub95.ezboard.com/binnoruukserver.showLocalUserPublicProfile?login=innoruuk>Innoruuk</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://www.ezboard.com/ezgfx/gicons/black_magentaspot.gif" BORDE